{"tid":2187730,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"［尋書] 求 少年間諜艾列克 全系列二手書","createTime":"2020-09-03T22:21:11.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-03T22:21:11.000Z","uid":34234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"b33fa5b159250f6359b5dc1509fa89ad3b89154d","tid":2187730,"uid":34234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T22:21:11.000Z","msg":"以前細個睇過頭兩本 覺得好好睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大個想睇返 點知自己又唔記得書名<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仲試過去圖書館搵哂所有翻譯小說 都係唔記得書名<br />\n<br />\n終於比我不斷係網上搵關鍵字 頭先比我搵得返！<br />\n<br />\n原來叫 少年間諜艾列克 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n可惜 我見網上好多絕哂版 無得買<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n求有心人放全系列 (求其一本都得) 二手書<br />\n<br />\n或者求推介邊到仲有得買/可以買到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n萬分感激<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}